snippet.title: We Are OFK - PlayStation Reveal
snippet.description:
From indie pop band OFK: We Are OFK follows the lives of four friends in their 20s as they attempt to break into the music business, fall in and out of love, and figure out how to pay rent and make art in Los Angeles. Wishlist Now on Steam! http://ofk.cool/steam

We Are OFK, the new interactive series coming soon to Steam!
•   Wishlist on Steam: http://ofk.cool/steam
•   Stream "Follow/Unfollow" by OFK everywhere: http://ofk.cool
•   Twitter: https://twitter.com/OFKband
•   Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ofkband
•   Website: http://ofk.cool

Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCdUdli03uuvOHU1XZT0QuKw?sub_confirmation=1

"Follow/Unfollow"
Written and Produced by - Luna Shadows & Thomas Powers
Performed by - OFK
Mixed by - Beatriz Artola
Mastered by - Jett Galindo
Vocals by - Teddy Dief

We Are OFK original score composed and performed by Omniboi
